snippet.title: Destroy All Humans! 2 - Reprobed - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Crypto is back with a license to probe! Destroy All Humans! 2 - Reprobed is coming soon to PC, PlayStation 5, and Xbox Series S|X.

Take revenge on the KGB for blowing up your mothership. Disguise yourself as a human and read their minds to gain intel and infiltrate their society. Cause wide-scale destruction with your UFO all over the planet.

But be warned - you’ll have to form alliances with members of the very species you came to enslave.

- Pre-Order Here -
Steam: https://thqn.net/dah2-steam
PSN: https://thqn.net/dah2-psn
Xbox: https://thqn.net/dah2-xbox

- Links & Info -
Website: https://www.destroyallhumansgame.com
Discord: https://discord.gg/destroy

- Our Socials -
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/THQNordic

Facebook: https://facebook.com/destroyallhumansgame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/thqnordic
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/thqnordic

#DestroyAllHumans #LicencedToProbe
